ian police.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3271225038629087e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone's approval\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"the river's murky past\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"state violence\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"colonisation\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"notably the 1961 massacre\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"Algerians\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parisian police\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo and Macron have put their long-standing squabbles aside to devise a plan to 'cleanse' the polluted Seine, where swimming has been banned for over a century.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9075152500400446e-43, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3271225038629087e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their long-standing squabbles\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"a plan\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"over a century\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After investing US$1.4 billion to ready the Seine for theOlympics-mostly to prevent sewage leaks into the river-the Seine has finally passed daily water quality tests.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1602, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3271225038629087e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Seine\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"sewage leaks\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"daily water quality tests\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Donning a wetsuit and goggles, Hidalgo swam in the famed waterway last week as hundreds of onlookers cheered from the riverbanks, fulfilling a promise she made back in January.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5654139304264715e-17, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wetsuit\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"goggles\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"the famed waterway\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"onlookers\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverbanks\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"a promise\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Paris, hosting theOlympicswimming events in the Seine is a momentous occasion, but for many, the river's legacy cannot escape the legacy of the 1961 massacre.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7558170005030704e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1885, \"end\": 1890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3271225038629087e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"a momentous occasion\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"the river's legacy\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"the legacy\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1961 massacre\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the evening of 17 October 1961, men, women, and children-French citizens of Algeria-peacefully marched towards Paris to protest a discriminatory nighttime curfew targeting Algerians in the Paris region.\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2111, \"end\": 2116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7558170005030704e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2189, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7558170005030704e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"17 October\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"children-French citizens\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"a discriminatory nighttime curfew\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"Algerians\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the demonstration turned into a massacre.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the demonstration\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"a massacre\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That night, French police beat, killed, and threw between 200-300 Algerians into the Seine, with about 12,000 Algerians arrested in the crackdown.\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.795573412003505e-46, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"beg